2. bacnet-transport (vendored, patched)
   Location: crates/proto-bacnet/vendor/bacnet-transport
   Origin: the rusty-bacnet project.
   License: MIT (see crates/proto-bacnet/vendor/bacnet-transport/LICENSE).
   Patch: keeps the broadcast destination port at 47808 when the local bind
   port is ephemeral (port = 0); upstream sends broadcasts to the ephemeral
   bind port, which breaks BACnet Who-Is discovery from an ephemeral-port client.
   The netix-republisher binary repo vendors its own copy of this patched crate.
